{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Merci Monsieur le Pr\u00e9sident.", "start": 0.616, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "Ce matin,", "start": 1.666, "duration": 0.367}, {"text": "nous parlons de secours en mer", "start": 2.033, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "et de politique d'asile.", "start": 3.383, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "Bien s\u00fbr, bien s\u00fbr,", "start": 4.533, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "il faut sauver les gens qui se noient.", "start": 6.2, "duration": 2.216}, {"text": "Personne ne le conteste, ici.", "start": 8.433, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "Mais le mieux, c'est encore d'\u00e9viter", "start": 10.333, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "qu'ils risquent leur vie.", "start": 11.633, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "Qu'est-ce qui endeuille aujourd'hui", "start": 12.583, "duration": 1.783}, {"text": "la mer M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e ?", "start": 14.366, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "C'est notre impuissance collective", "start": 16.033, "duration": 2.017}, {"text": "qui fait que si", "start": 18.05, "duration": 0.566}, {"text": "quelqu'un arrive \u00e0 entrer ill\u00e9galement", "start": 18.616, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "en Europe,", "start": 20.266, "duration": 0.367}, {"text": "il est certain d'y rester toujours.", "start": 20.633, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "C'est la d\u00e9mission de gouvernements,", "start": 22.283, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "dont le gouvernement fran\u00e7ais,", "start": 23.566, "duration": 1.384}, {"text": "dont la d\u00e9cision", "start": 24.95, "duration": 0.633}, {"text": "d'accueillir ce bateau est", "start": 25.583, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "la publicit\u00e9 dont r\u00eavaient", "start": 26.516, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "les r\u00e9seaux de passeurs.", "start": 27.716, "duration": 1.284}, {"text": "C'est la complicit\u00e9 de certaines ONG,", "start": 29.0, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "dont il est av\u00e9r\u00e9", "start": 30.733, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "qu'elles sont en contact \u00e9troit", "start": 31.483, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "avec ces fili\u00e8res de traite", "start": 33.083, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "d'\u00eatres humains.", "start": 34.183, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "C'est le d\u00e9tournement", "start": 35.15, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "de nos principes", "start": 36.016, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "par des jurisprudences abusives", "start": 36.683, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "qui rendent impuissantes nos lois.", "start": 38.183, "duration": 1.983}, {"text": "C'est l'acharnement", "start": 40.166, "duration": 0.684}, {"text": "de ceux qui, \u00e0 la Commission", "start": 40.85, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "parfois ou au Parlement,", "start": 42.133, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "ont attaqu\u00e9 sans rel\u00e2che", "start": 43.4, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "la direction de Frontex,", "start": 44.45, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "non parce", "start": 45.45, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "qu'elle ne faisait pas son travail,", "start": 46.133, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "mais parce qu'elle faisait son travail.", "start": 47.666, "duration": 1.85}, {"text": "Nous ne faisons m\u00eame plus semblant", "start": 49.516, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "de combattre ces r\u00e9seaux de passeurs,", "start": 50.683, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "la mafia la plus criminelle du monde,", "start": 52.283, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "qui gagne", "start": 54.083, "duration": 0.383}, {"text": "des milliards", "start": 54.466, "duration": 0.484}, {"text": "d'euros gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 notre passivit\u00e9.", "start": 54.95, "duration": 1.833}, {"text": "Ce n'est pas d'abord", "start": 56.783, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "parce qu'ils fuient la guerre", "start": 57.466, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "ou la mis\u00e8re", "start": 58.4, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "que les gens se noient en M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e.", "start": 59.266, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "Ceux qui partent", "start": 60.583, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "sont ceux", "start": 61.516, "duration": 0.334}, {"text": "qui ont d\u00e9j\u00e0 assez de moyens", "start": 61.85, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "pour payer la travers\u00e9e.", "start": 63.083, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "Mais nous,", "start": 64.616, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "nous n'avons pas le droit,", "start": 65.333, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "m\u00eame si nous les comprenons,", "start": 66.616, "duration": 1.75}, {"text": "nous n'avons pas le droit au cynisme,", "start": 68.366, "duration": 1.384}, {"text": "cach\u00e9 derri\u00e8re les beaux discours,", "start": 69.75, "duration": 1.316}, {"text": "qui comptent sur les forces vives", "start": 71.066, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "des pays en d\u00e9veloppement,", "start": 72.3, "duration": 1.25}, {"text": "pour faire chez nous", "start": 73.55, "duration": 0.716}, {"text": "le travail que nous ne voulons", "start": 74.266, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "plus faire,", "start": 75.166, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "ou que nos entreprises", "start": 75.916, "duration": 0.784}, {"text": "ne veulent plus payer comme il faut.", "start": 76.7, "duration": 1.683}, {"text": "\"L'Europe est une soci\u00e9t\u00e9", "start": 78.383, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "vieillissante\", avez-vous dit, Madame", "start": 79.5, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "la Commissaire.", "start": 80.783, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "\"L'Europe a besoin de personnes de tous", "start": 81.8, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "niveaux de qualification\",", "start": 83.15, "duration": 0.983}, {"text": "je vous cite,", "start": 84.133, "duration": 0.883}, {"text": "\"l'Union europ\u00e9enne \u00e9largira", "start": 85.016, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "les possibilit\u00e9s de migrations.\"", "start": 86.416, "duration": 1.867}, {"text": "Mais cette logique utilitariste,", "start": 88.283, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "derri\u00e8re des grandes le\u00e7ons de morale,", "start": 89.566, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "qui pr\u00e9tend s'inqui\u00e9ter", "start": 91.166, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "de la souffrance", "start": 92.066, "duration": 0.567}, {"text": "des plus lointains,", "start": 92.633, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "elle n'\u00e9coute pas", "start": 93.383, "duration": 0.933}, {"text": "la souffrance des plus proches,", "start": 94.316, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "des plus pauvres,", "start": 95.45, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "des plus vuln\u00e9rables", "start": 96.35, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "dans nos propres pays,", "start": 97.1, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "ceux qui vivent directement", "start": 98.3, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "les tensions terribles,", "start": 99.35, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "n\u00e9es du d\u00e9ni", "start": 100.7, "duration": 0.566}, {"text": "de cette politique migratoire", "start": 101.266, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "irresponsable.", "start": 102.683, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "La solidarit\u00e9 europ\u00e9enne", "start": 103.85, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "doit consister \u00e0 r\u00e9pondre", "start": 105.016, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "ensemble \u00e0 ce d\u00e9fi, non pas en g\u00e9rant", "start": 106.316, "duration": 2.184}, {"text": "notre impuissance,", "start": 108.5, "duration": 0.783}, {"text": "mais en y mettant enfin fin.", "start": 109.283, "duration": 2.167}, {"text": "Merci beaucoup.", "start": 111.45, "duration": 0.55}]}